      <trans-unit id="stack.lead" datatype="html">
        <source> No colecciono frameworks. Profundizo en los que eleijo con criterio y entiendo sus trade-offs en contextos reales. </source>
        <target> I don't collect frameworks. I go deep on the ones I choose deliberately and understand their trade-offs in real contexts. </target>
      </trans-unit>
